      <dl>
        <dlentry>
          <dt>XDITA</dt>
          <dd><p><xmlelement>dl</xmlelement></p></dd>
          </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt>HDITA</dt>
          <dd><p><xmlelement>dl</xmlelement></p></dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt>MDITA (extended profile)</dt>
          <dd>
            <p>A single-line term followed by a colon (<codeph>:</codeph>) and the definition for that term, following
              the <xref href="https://michelf.ca/projects/php-markdown/extra/#def-list"
                format="html" scope="external">PHP Markdown Extra syntax for definition
              list</xref></p>
          </dd>
        </dlentry>
      </dl>
